https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4UMVVLQ1rd1SBVS84KNJaAnV4qW.jpg Five high school cheerleaders drive out to a rural mansion to spend the weekend. They hear a thirty year-old urban legend about a young boy who killed his family and used their blood in his juvenile artwork. While exploring an old farmhouse on the property they discover that the boy never left his home and has grown into a sick and twisted man. A Brush With Death
